# GABC snippets for vim-snippets or UltiSnips

# Response markings
snippet a/. "Antiphon Response" b
<sp>A/</sp>.
endsnippet

snippet ca/. "Colored Antiphon Response" b
<c><sp>A/</sp>.</c>
endsnippet

snippet r/. "Responsory Response" b
<sp>R/</sp>.
endsnippet

snippet cr/. "Colored Responsory Response" b
<c><sp>R/</sp>.</c>
endsnippet

snippet v/. "Verse" b
<sp>V/</sp>.
endsnippet

snippet cv/. "Colored Verse" b
<c><sp>V/</sp>.</c>
endsnippet

